REFERENCE           VADER3
LANG_ENGLISH        "Commander, tear this ship apart until you've found those plans!\nAnd bring me the passengers! I want them alive!"
LANG_CHINESE        "指挥官,就是把飞船拆碎了也要把设计图找出来\n还有把乘客带来见我!我要活的!"

REFERENCE           VADER4
LANG_ENGLISH        "Don't act so surprised, Your Highness. You weren't on any mercy mission this time. Several transmissions were beamed to this ship by rebel spies. I want to know what happened to the plans they sent you."
LANG_CHINESE        "不要装得这么惊讶,殿下。你可不是在干什么好事，叛军的间谍向你们的飞船定向传输了若干信息，我想知道他们发送给你的那些信息是怎么回事。"

REFERENCE           VADER5
LANG_ENGLISH        "You are part of the Rebel Alliance and a traitor.\nTake her away!"
LANG_CHINESE        "你是叛军的一员，和帝国的叛徒\n把她带走"

REFERENCE           VADER6
LANG_ENGLISH        "I have traced the Rebel spies to her.\nNow she is my only link to finding their secret base."
