LANG_ENGLISH        "Leave that to me.\nSend a distress signal, and then inform the senate that all aboard were killed."
LANG_CHINESE        "都交给我吧\n发出一个求救信号...然后告诉议会所有船上的人都死了,"

REFERENCE           VADER8
LANG_ENGLISH        "She must have hidden the plans in the escape pod. Send a detachment down to retrieve them. See to it personally, Commander. There'll be no one to stop us this time."
LANG_CHINESE        "她一定把计划藏在那个逃生舱了.派遣一支冲锋队去把它找回来.指挥官,在我个人看来,这次不会有任何人阻止我们"

